Next, I'll work on the **WeatherForm component** (highest priority todo). This will allow users to input a city name and trigger the weather API fetch.

I'll create `WeatherForm.tsx` in `frontend/src/components/`. It will:
- Accept city, setCity, setWeather, setLoading, setError as props
- Use Chakra UI for a clean form
